expression: body
---
Update GaussClaw to the latest signed release. (Hermes parity: `hermes update`.)

Usage: update [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --channel <CHANNEL>
          Release channel
          
          [default: stable]

      --dry-run
          Show what would be installed without performing the upgrade

  -h, --help
          Print help
